                "invention-title": [
                    "Process and device for preparing methanol through catalytic hydrogenation of carbon dioxide",
                    "一种二氧化碳催化加氢制甲醇的工艺和装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of methanol preparation through carbon dioxide hydrogenation, in particular to a process and a device for methanol preparation through carbon dioxide catalytic hydrogenation. The process comprises the following steps: compressing a mixed raw material gas of carbon dioxide and hydrogen, mixing the compressed mixed raw material gas with a recycle gas, carrying out heat exchange and heating on the mixed gas, and feeding the heated mixed gas into a methanol synthesis tower for methanol synthesis; the synthesized gas provides a heat source for an atmospheric tower waste heat reboiler; carrying out gas-liquid separation on the cooled gas in a separator; and returning the separated gas phase part to the methanol synthesis tower to continue methanol synthesis, separating light components from the liquid phase through flash evaporation, and separating dissolved carbon dioxide, hydrogen, methane and the like from crude alcohol in a pre-rectifying tower. According to the invention, the specific contradictory problems of low synthesis heat release and high energy consumption of rectification separation and purification of a device for preparing methanol through carbon dioxide hydrogenation are solved, and external supply of steam is not needed. Multiple-effect heat coupling of the pre-rectifying tower, the normal-pressure rectifying tower and the vacuum rectifying tower is achieved, and comprehensive energy consumption is low."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及二氧化碳加氢制甲醇技术领域，具体为一种二氧化碳催化加氢制甲醇的工艺和装置。该工艺包括以下步骤：二氧化碳和氢气的混合原料气经压缩后与循环气混合，混合气经换热和加热后进入甲醇合成塔进行甲醇合成；合成后的气体为常压塔余热再沸器提供热源；降温后的气体去分离器进行气液分离；分离后的气相部分返回到甲醇合成塔继续进行甲醇合成，液相经闪蒸分离轻组分后，粗醇进入预精馏塔分离溶解的二氧化碳、氢气、甲烷等。本发明解决了二氧化碳加氢制甲醇装置特有的合成放热量低，精馏分离提纯能耗高的矛盾问题，不需要外供蒸汽。实现预精馏塔、常压精馏塔和真空精馏塔的多效热量耦合，综合能耗低。"
                }
            ]
